    "text": "i didn't have to wait that long to find"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.919,
    "endTime": 433.36,
    "text": "an answer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.36,
    "endTime": 436.24,
    "text": "six months after that first visit he"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.24,
    "endTime": 439.199,
    "text": "invited me back to new york"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.199,
    "endTime": 441.039,
    "text": "the designers of the brooklyn bridge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.039,
    "endTime": 443.36,
    "text": "they had their share of bad luck"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.36,
    "endTime": 445.039,
    "text": "john roebling he died shortly after the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.039,
    "endTime": 447.199,
    "text": "bridges construction began his son"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.199,
    "endTime": 448.96,
    "text": "washington took over but he suffered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.96,
    "endTime": 451.12,
    "text": "from decompression sickness his wife"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.12,
    "endTime": 453.039,
    "text": "emily became the surrogate executive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.039,
    "endTime": 454.479,
    "text": "engineer who oversaw the bridge's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.479,
    "endTime": 456.08,
    "text": "completion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.08,
    "endTime": 457.599,
    "text": "father and son"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.599,
    "endTime": 459.36,
    "text": "john in washington"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.36,
    "endTime": 461.44,
    "text": "done in by their work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.44,
    "endTime": 463.199,
    "text": "it was this sunny day in may and my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.199,
    "endTime": 464.96,
    "text": "father and i sat in the shadow of that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.96,
    "endTime": 466.72,
    "text": "brooklyn bridge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.72,
    "endTime": 468.479,
    "text": "but our lives followed the roblings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.479,
    "endTime": 469.919,
    "text": "father and son"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.919,
    "endTime": 472.639,
    "text": "done in by our work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.639,
    "endTime": 474.639,
    "text": "my father thought that her friends in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474.639,
    "endTime": 476.639,
    "text": "church would would carry her through her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.639,
    "endTime": 479.28,
    "text": "transition and they did not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.28,
    "endTime": 481.36,
    "text": "they ditched her and they clung to me i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.36,
    "endTime": 482.72,
    "text": "was the pastor of a new church in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.72,
    "endTime": 484.72,
    "text": "brooklyn this wonderful group of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.72,
    "endTime": 486.639,
    "text": "forward-thinking people and yet we were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.639,
    "endTime": 488.56,
    "text": "financially tied to really conservative"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.56,
    "endTime": 489.84,
    "text": "churches"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.84,
    "endTime": 492.879,
    "text": "to hold space for paula and jeopardizing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.879,
    "endTime": 494.8,
    "text": "our own church's livelihood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.8,
    "endTime": 496.56,
    "text": "i sort of straddled the line between"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.56,
    "endTime": 497.44,
    "text": "these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.44,
    "endTime": 499.84,
    "text": "warring worlds and so i said to my dad i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.84,
    "endTime": 501.68,
    "text": "said dad you know i still live and work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.68,
    "endTime": 503.759,
    "text": "in your old world is it is it possible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.759,
    "endTime": 505.12,
    "text": "that you might extend an olive branch"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.12,
    "endTime": 507.199,
    "text": "for my sake"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.199,
    "endTime": 508.8,
    "text": "and her response"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.8,
    "endTime": 511.84,
    "text": "was impassioned"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.84,
    "endTime": 513.518,
    "text": "you said to me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.519,
    "endTime": 515.76,
    "text": "do you have any idea what it feels like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.76,
    "endTime": 517.68,
    "text": "to finally show yourself to your true"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.68,
    "endTime": 519.839,
    "text": "friends and have them completely reject"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 519.839,
    "endTime": 522.399,
    "text": "you to ask you to live a lie do you know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.399,
    "endTime": 524.959,
    "text": "what that feels like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.959,
    "endTime": 528.56,
    "text": "and i didn't know what that felt like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.56,
    "endTime": 531.2,
    "text": "but i knew i had a decision to make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 531.2,
    "endTime": 533.04,
    "text": "it was the decision to continue down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.04,
    "endTime": 535.12,
    "text": "that narrow path through nights but for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.12,
    "endTime": 536.88,
    "text": "the first time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.88,
    "endTime": 539.6,
    "text": "i caught a glimpse of light"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.6,
    "endTime": 542.16,
    "text": "could not ask my father to be anything"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.16,
    "endTime": 546.44,
    "text": "other than her true self"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.24,
    "endTime": 555.2,
    "text": "so as we sat by the river that day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.2,
    "endTime": 557.68,
    "text": "jonathan talked about his pain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.68,
    "endTime": 561.04,
    "text": "his suffering his grief his confusion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.04,
    "endTime": 563.12,
    "text": "he brought all of himself to that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.12,
    "endTime": 566.08,
    "text": "conversation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 567.12,
    "endTime": 570.32,
    "text": "and it tore at me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.2,
    "endTime": 576.12,
    "text": "to be the cause of such pain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.32,
    "endTime": 577.76,
    "text": "but as he talked there was something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577.76,
    "endTime": 580.16,
    "text": "redemptive going on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.16,
    "endTime": 583.2,
    "text": "full of tension but possibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.2,
    "endTime": 587.04,
    "text": "grounded in that narrow path"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.04,
    "endTime": 588.72,
    "text": "he said this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588.72,
    "endTime": 592.0,
    "text": "is always going to be hard it always"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.0,
    "endTime": 594.64,
    "text": "will be but dad"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.64,
    "endTime": 596.8,
    "text": "i love you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.8,
    "endTime": 599.6,
    "text": "you know my son is the best of me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.6,
    "endTime": 600.88,
    "text": "and more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.88,
    "endTime": 603.44,
    "text": "he's bold and strong"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.44,
    "endTime": 604.64,
    "text": "sensitive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.64,
    "endTime": 606.64,
    "text": "and thoughtful"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.64,
    "endTime": 609.68,
    "text": "i guess you could say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.0,
    "endTime": 614.0,
    "text": "he's an alpha male who's gentile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.399,
    "endTime": 616.079,
    "text": "it was time for my daughters to meet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.079,
    "endTime": 616.839,
    "text": "their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.839,
    "endTime": 618.959,
    "text": "paula we went back to my apartment and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.959,
    "endTime": 620.56,
